{"tid":1612010,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"下次遊行或者集會, 請留返俾和理勇","createTime":"2019-10-02T06:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:12:13.000Z","uid":56546,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee72fa8e11aba164b356565100b3935ef407a9ec","tid":1612010,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"前線真勇武派<br />\n我地唔需要你地保護<br />\n千其唔好再出現係遊行地點<br />\n<br />\n唔係因為不和或者恐懼所以要分開<br />\n相反係因為大家都相信大家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請你地以多個小隊, 遊擊式咁係唔同地區支援（獅鳥, 爆玻璃, 爆港鐵咩都好）<br />\n請揾信得過嘅人組隊, 同時小隊型式亦都較難有臥底入侵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然未必敢衝, 但和理勇都一樣有勇氣同大家去擋子彈"},{"pid":"f5c325f179e92a9a0773212f7223d803b11721a5","tid":1612010,"uid":260296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"多區開花<br />\n一區遊行<br />\n<br />\n諗得過"},{"pid":"e626f46d07be342e51b5ab863fc1d81a7ba9b453","tid":1612010,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EF2JpI5XUAIXD93?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEF2JpI5XUAIXD93%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=44c19fd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c332276008ed356acc40840dc5083c8f4b7e72b","tid":1612010,"uid":56546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f5c325f179e92a9a0773212f7223d803b11721a5","tid":1612010,"uid":260296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"多區開花<br />\n一區遊行<br />\n<br />\n諗得過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n<br />\n遊行時嘅新前線<br />\n亦都可以有機會訓練成為勇武"},{"pid":"4dd6c1d702c005b59f86b95ecba4e3be1b2786b7","tid":1612010,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2180e234da33d64ab940ac531f7b09ed20c2dbad","tid":1612010,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>假若昨天那位中五生真的被射殺，那又如何？<br />\n<br />\n大家會更悲憤，但只限於室內，只限於網絡上，你們的能耐不過在一個小小的黑色方格內打上五六句罵人說話而已，換句話說，網絡有效地宣洩和吸收了大部分的義憤，讓它化為虛無。<br />\n<br />\n你們一邊政府吶喊：是你教我和平抗議沒有用的；一邊卻用一個更無用的辦法去和平抗議。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n［致香港人：你地悲憤完未？］<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612021\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612021</a>"},{"pid":"405de277a71868dfa6063a92c11575aba0ad44d0","tid":1612010,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89cec4424369936a5cd1e8efd635c833c8656fa3","tid":1612010,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"don't need the protection, protect yourselves"}]}